title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

The following was found on a bottle of Tylenol brand Arthritis Pain medication: “do not use for fore than 10 days unless directed by a doctor under 18 years of age” [Submitted by Dale E. Claes, Fresno CA]
